<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Tribute Page</title>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial;
      margin: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    /* Navigation Bar */
    nav {
      background-color: black;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      margin: 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: yellow;
    }

    /* Header */
    header {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #333;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    /* Section */
    section {
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px;
      background-color: white;
      border: 2px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    /* Image */
    img {
      display: block;
      margin: auto;
      width: 200px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid black;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: black;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
    }
  </style>

</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#">Home</a>
  <a href="#">About</a>
  <a href="#">Achievements</a>
  <a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>

<header>
  <h1>Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam</h1>
  <p>Missile Man of India</p>
</header>

<section>
  <h2>About</h2>
  <img src="https://allworldspresidents.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Abdul-Kalam.jpg.png" alt="A.P.J.Abdul Kalam" width="150" height="150">

  <p>
    Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam was a great scientist and the 11th President of India. 
    He inspired millions with his knowledge and humility.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Achievements</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Worked on India's missile programs</li>
    <li>President of India (2002–2007)</li>
    <li>Bharat Ratna Award Winner</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>Made for Web Designing Project</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
 
